title: Physical Medicine & Rehabilitation Excellence in Leadership Fund
description: To provide faculty support in the Department of Physical Medicine & Rehabilitation with the goal of establishing an endowed chair at the Anschutz Medical Campus.  If $25,000 is reached within five years, the funds will be invested in a pure endowment.
